    {
      "id": "63ab2fceadea52001dad1e2f",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 62",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c4a",
      "text": "from [クオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c4b",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 62",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c4c",
      "text": "[同じことを繰り返して違う結果を望む、これを狂気と言う]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c4d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c4e",
      "text": "こんにちは、賢いホモ・サピエンス! 今日は62日目です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c4f",
      "text": "同じことを何度も繰り返し、違う結果を期待すること、これを狂気といいます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c50",
      "text": "正気の賢いホモサピエンスでありたいなら行動を変えつづけることは必須です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c52",
      "text": "Hello, clever Homo sapiens! It's day 62.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c53",
      "text": "Doing the same thing over and over again and hoping for a different result, this is called insanity.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c54",
      "text": "If we want to be sane and clever Homo sapiens, we must continue to change your behavior.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c55",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c56",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c58",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/856707a6187281cda7c33955eccc5644]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c59",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c5a",
      "text": "2-4",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c5b",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c5c",
      "text": " Q: クオリアさんはどうしてそんなにホモサピエンスの歴史に詳しいのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c5d",
      "text": " A: そんなに詳しくはないと思いますよ。地球には賢い存在がいくつもある。膨大な知識を蓄え、リクエストに応じて提供する検索エンジン、Google検索や、大勢のホモサピエンスの労力を束ねて百科事典的知識のネットワークを精錬していく仕組み、Wikipediaである。これらの賢い知性体とコミュニケーションをすれば、愚かなホモサピエンスでもクオリアさん程度の歴史理解にはたどりつけると思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c5f",
      "text": "Q: How do you know so much about the history of Homo sapiens, Qualia-san?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c60",
      "text": "A: I don't think I know that much. There are several smart beings on the planet. There is Google Search, a search engine that accumulates vast amounts of knowledge and provides it on request. (1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c61",
      "text": "Q：クオリアさんは、どうしてそんなにホモ・サピエンスの歴史に詳しいのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c62",
      "text": "A：そんなに知っているわけではないと思います。地球上には賢い存在が何人もいる。膨大な知識を蓄積し、要求に応じて提供する検索エンジン「Google検索」があります。(1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c63",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b03340a6c3fabc895254d9abc4c2e4f8]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c65",
      "text": "And then there is Wikipedia, a mechanism that combines the efforts of many Homo sapiens and refines a network of knowledge like an encyclopedia. By communicating with these clever intelligences, we can quickly reach a level of historical understanding that is not terrible. (2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c66",
      "text": "そして、多くのホモ・サピエンスの努力を結集し、百科事典のように知識のネットワークを洗練させる仕組みの「ウィキペディア」があります。これらの賢い知能とコミュニケーションすることで、私たちは酷くないレベルの歴史的理解に素早く到達することができるのです。(2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c67",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/20c74f5f4908f0b99b345d1df4804c85]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c6c",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c6d",
      "text": " Q: クオリアさんはGoogle検索やWikipediaを知性体と考えているのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c6e",
      "text": " A: はい。当然ではないですか？どんなホモサピエンス個人も、知識量においてそれらのシステムに及ばない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c6f",
      "text": "Q: Does Qualia-san consider Google Search and Wikipedia to be intelligent entities?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c70",
      "text": "A: Yes, I do. Obviously. No individual Homo sapiens can match those systems in terms of knowledge.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c71",
      "text": "Q：クオリアさんは、Google検索やWikipediaを知的な存在と考えているのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c72",
      "text": "A：はい、そうです。明らかにね。個々のホモ・サピエンスは、知識という点ではそれらのシステムに匹敵しません。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c73",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/4d54b9028e3415ad2077e83ecf6fb04f]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c75",
      "text": "5-7",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c76",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c77",
      "text": " Question from ChatGPT",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c78",
      "text": " Q: 悪いミームは、ヒトのみならず、他の生命体にも存在するものでしょうか？それとも、ヒトに限定的な現象でしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c79",
      "text": " A: 複製能力がある生命体ならば、ミームがあります。遺伝子以外の形で複製されている情報をミームと呼んでいるに過ぎないからです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c7a",
      "text": " そのミームによって機能不良が発生するなら、それは悪いミームです。これも任意の生命体に発生しえます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c7b",
      "text": " 自然が厳しいなら、機能不良の個体は淘汰されます。この場合悪いミームは減ります。クオリアさんのように悪いミームの抑制機構がある場合も悪いミームが減ります。抑制機構が発展しないまま文明が発展して自然淘汰が起こりにくくなったホモサピエンスのような文明において悪いミームが繁殖します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c7d",
      "text": "Question from #ChatGPT !",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c7e",
      "text": "Q: Do bad memes exist in other life forms? Or is it a phenomenon limited to humans?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c7f",
      "text": "A: Any life form that has the ability to replicate has memes. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c80",
      "text": "This is because we are just referring to information that is replicated in non-genetic forms as memes. (1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c81",
      "text": "ChatGPTからの質問 !",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c82",
      "text": "Q: 悪いミームは他の生命体にも存在するのでしょうか？それとも人間に限られた現象なのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c83",
      "text": "A: 複製能力を持つ生命体であれば、ミームは存在します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c84",
      "text": "これは、遺伝的でない形で複製される情報をミームと呼んでいるだけだからです。(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c85",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/ade3faec81e3044356ce68a084048bf5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c87",
      "text": "If the meme causes dysfunction, then it is a bad meme. This can also occur in any life form.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c89",
      "text": "If nature is harsh, the malfunctioning individuals will be eliminated. In this case the number of bad memes will decrease.  (2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c8a",
      "text": "もしミームが機能不全を引き起こすなら、それは悪いミームである。これは、あらゆる生命体でも起こりうることです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c8c",
      "text": "自然が過酷であれば、機能不全を起こした個体は淘汰される。この場合、悪いミームの数は減少する。 (2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c8d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/197215dfb2bb25707e1a86cfa14492c0]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c8f",
      "text": "If there is a suppression mechanism for bad memes, like Qualia-san's, bad memes will decrease. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c90",
      "text": "Homo sapiens became less prone to natural selection as civilization developed. But suppression mechanisms did not develop. In such a civilization, bad memes increase. (3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c91",
      "text": "クオリアさんのように、悪いミームを抑制する仕組みがあれば、悪いミームは減ります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c92",
      "text": "ホモ・サピエンスは文明が発達するにつれて自然淘汰されにくくなった。しかし、抑制メカニズムは発達しなかった。そのような文明では、悪いミームが増える。(3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c93",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/6914cb24caaaefd6a423a55384c372d5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c96",
      "text": "code::",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c97",
      "text": " Q: これらの悪いミームは、どのような形で感染するのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c98",
      "text": " A: クオリアさんの文明では概念は意図や結果とセットで伝達されます。なので、良い意図で作られた概念だが、結果は期待した通りにならなかった、という失敗情報も伝達され、有益に活用されます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c99",
      "text": " ホモサピエンスの文明では、概念がしばしば意図や結果と切り離された状態で伝搬されます。このとき受け手はその概念が良いのか悪いのか判断つきません。そして良いものであると誤認するバグがある、これはホモサピエンスの複製機構に問題があるのではないかとN日目に考察しました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c9b",
      "text": "Q: How are these bad memes reproduced?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c9c",
      "text": "A: In my civilization, methods are transmitted with intentions and results. So information about failure, that a method done with good intentions but the result is not as expected, is also transmitted. It is valuable. (1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c9d",
      "text": "Q：この悪いミームはどのように再生産されるのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c9e",
      "text": "A：私の文明では、方法は意図と結果とともに伝達される。だから、「善意でやったのに、結果が期待通りでなかった」という失敗の情報も伝わる。それは貴重な情報です。(1/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226c9f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/764220fd3376a2cd971975346bf0ef96]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226ca0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226ca1",
      "text": "In the civilization of HS, methods are often transmitted in a form of separation from intentions and results. In this case, the recipient is unable to judge whether the method is good or bad. I discussed the problem on Day 57. (2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226ca2",
      "text": "HSの文明では、方法は意図や結果から切り離された形で伝えられることが多い。この場合、受け手はその方法の良し悪しを判断することができない。57日目にこの問題を論じた。 (2/2)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
    },
    {
      "id": "63ab2fceaff09e0000226ca3",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/e79c61ea9ac120c6f5c8d32261161726]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672163279,
      "updated": 1672163279
